{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5c7a9d6dbc","title":"甘肃省委对“关于开展‘小秋收’运动紧急指示”的补充通知","origin":"甘肃省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a27e1cff2b","index":0,"year":1960,"month":11,"day":6,"articleId":"5c7a9d6dbc"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"89ce1177d8","type":"title","text":"甘肃省委对“关于开展‘小秋收’运动紧急指示”的补充通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5c7a9d6dbc"},{"id":"a0eac5d7b0","type":"appellation","text":"各地、市委，自治州委，各县(市)委并即转各公社党委、大队总支、生产队支部：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5c7a9d6dbc"},{"id":"5a2d94b542","type":"paragraph","text":"现在对省委十月三十日发出的关于开展小秋收运动的指示，作如下说明和补充：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5c7a9d6dbc"},{"id":"87a71d378c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、“要求资源丰富的地方按人口平均搞五十斤，一般地区每人搞三十斤。”这只是一个争取数字，不是硬性任务，各地可以不受这个限制，能多搞的地方，力争多搞，多多益善；资源困难的地方，搞十斤、二十斤也好。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5c7a9d6dbc"},{"id":"46bb98583f","type":"paragraph","text":"二、今年的小秋收一定要实事求是，一定要运回过秤才算数，不得虚报浮夸，而且省报和地方报纸都不许公布全省和一个地区的总数字。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5c7a9d6dbc"},{"id":"2e43bd78d5","type":"paragraph","text":" 甘肃省委1960年11月6日(甘肃省档案馆91—4—695卷)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5c7a9d6dbc"}],"page":{"id":"c5072eec5f","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"5c7a9d6dbc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}